mahābalaparākrama iti pratibhānakūṭaḥ | mahānti ca tāni balāni ceti daśa tathāgatabalāni sthānāsthānajñānādīni vakṣyamāṇāni teṣu parākramo vīryārambho yasya sa mahābalaparākramaḥ ||

<commentary>mahābhavetyādi | tatra mahābhavādrisaṃbhetteti mahāsthāmaprāptaḥ | bhavaḥ paṇcopādānaskandhāḥ | ta evādrir ajñānaśailatvāt | tasya samyagaviparītajñānalābhād bhañjanaśīlaḥ saṃbhettā | mahāṃś cāsau bhavādrisaṃbhettā ca mahābhavādrisaṃbhettā || mahāvajradharo ghana iti sarvāpāyañjahaḥ | mahāvajraṃ samantabhadrajñānaṃ tad dhārayatīti mahāvajradharaḥ | nibiḍatvān mūrtimattvāc ca ghanaḥ || mahākrūro mahāraudra iti sarvaśokatamonirghātamatiḥ | mahāṃś cāsau krūraś ca mahākrūraḥ | durdāntānāṃ sattvānāṃ mahākrodharūpasaṃdarśanāt | mahāraudra iti | śānto 'py asau bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ sattvavinayavaśād raudratām api darśayatīti || mahābhayabhayaṃkara iti jālinīprabhaḥ | mahābhayo mahābhairavarūpadhārī śaṃkara iti | tasyāpi bhayaṃ karotīti mahābhayabhayaṃkaraḥ ||</commentary>

mahāvidyetyādi | tatra mahāvidyottamo nātha iti candraprabhaḥ | mahatyaś ca tā vidyāś ca mahāvidyāś catasro dhāraṇyo granthārthamantramudrātmikāḥ |
